data.title: Robert Ford
data.meta_description: Robert Ford. Actor: Svet bez hranic. Robert Ford was born on 5 March 1887 in Mladá Boleslav, Bohemia, Austria-Hungary [now Czech Republic]. He was an actor, known for Svet bez hranic (1931), Bílá vrána (1938) and Zwei höllische Tage (1928). He died on 22 July 1949 in Prague, Czechoslovakia [now Czech Republic].
data.text: Robert Ford was born on March 5, 1887 in Mladá Boleslav, Bohemia, Austria-Hungary [now Czech Republic]. He was an actor, known for Svet bez hranic (1931), Bílá vrána (1938) and Zwei höllische Tage (1928). He died on July 22, 1949 in Prague, Czechoslovakia [now Czech Republic].
